  "text": "Based on combined genomic and transcriptomic information from 6 patients, with tumor stage Dukes A, B, C and D, respectively (n=24), a recent study showed the presence of THSD1 in 17 genes that have been expressed in Dukes D that may be relevant to tumor progression [CITATION_1] .",
